   <h2>Robert Herjavec</h2>
   <div>
     Born: September 14, 1962
   </div>
   <div>
     Primarily Works for: CEO of The Herjavec Group
   </div>
   <div>
   University: University of Toronto
   </div>
   <h4>Biography<h4>
     <p>Robert Herjavec is a Croatian-Canadian business man, that is a panelist on the show Shark Tank and the Dragons' Den. </p> 
     <h4>Notable Contribution</h4>
     <ul>
       <li>1990 - Founded BRAK systems, a Canadian integrator of internet security software. from the basement of his home.</li>
       <li>2003 - Robert founded the Herjavec Group, a secuirty solutions integrator, reseller, ad managed service provider.</li>
       <li>2006 - Appointed to the panel of venture capitlists on Dragons' Den. </li>
     </ul>
     <h4>Famous Quote:</h4>
     <blockquote>"A goal without a deadline is just a dream."</blockquote>
